(72, 1, 0x323032302d30392d30332030303a30393a3039, 0x323032302d30392d30332030303a30393a3039, '<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>WHO: Vaccination is the administration of agent-specific, but safe, antigenic components that in vaccinated individuals can induce protective immunity against the corresponding infectious agent. </p><cite><a href=\"https://www.who.int/travel-advice/vaccines\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.who.int/travel-advice/vaccines\">https://www.who.int/travel-advice/vaccines</a></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'What is vaccine', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', 0x323032302d30392d30332030303a30393a3039, 0x323032302d30392d30332030303a30393a3039, '', 17, 'http://128.199.234.8/?p=72', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
